	<h1 class="title">巴黎恐怖袭击事件新细节浮出水面，ISIS到底做了什么？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Rukmini Callimachi, Alissa J. Rubin and Laure Fourquet</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-23 10:17:44 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/24311/medium/24311.jpg?1458695283" alt="" />			
	</div>
